As for the explosive growth thing, I completely and totally disagree.  This genre goes back WAY before UO and EQ (and Asherons Call which you forgot and is a competitor that EQ has already done well against).  Those were just the first games to have mass appeal.  It may very well be that there are quite a few periods of explosive growth left since all of the games populations *combined* total less than 1 million.<br>
